name: My Oh My...
description:
Wasn't hard to love you
Didn't have to try
Wasn't hard to love you
Didn't have to try
Held you for a little while
My oh, my oh, my
...


Lovers that darkness and modesty abhill, at the back of a pub. Ireland.
They were so sweet, so delicate to each other, I think I would remember them for the rest of my life.
